00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,557
Mr. Zhongfu!

352
00:16:06,557 --> 00:16:07,576
Hello sir.

353
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,376
What a coincidence!

354
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,736
Why are you in Beijing?

355
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:11,016
After Shanghai,

356
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:12,776
