357
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,760
Sit down. Sit down.

358
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:17,496
She had just passed the Peking University entrance exam,

359
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:19,336
But now Peking University doesn't accept female students.

360
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,416
So Bailan worked as a tutor in Dongjiaominxiang

361
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,696
