363
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,856
Today, she just got paid.

364
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,536
The two of us planned to come here to have a nice meal.

365
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:30,456
I didn't expect to meet you, sir.

366
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,896
What a coincidence!

367
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,176
You are at Peking University now.

368
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,416
