385
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,856
Have a nice meal.

386
00:16:58,880 --> 00:16:59,576
Yes.

387
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:02,296
Here, eat.

388
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:05,016
Go ahead, eat.

389
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:07,080
Thank you, sir.

