395
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:02,856
This is a method I've just learned from the labouring masses.

396
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:05,000
It's exceptionally delightful.

397
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:08,440
An absolute delight!

398
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,776
Hurry up and eat. Gotta pick up a fare.

399
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,816
What fare?

400
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:19,336
Are you pulling a rickshaw?

401
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:21,656
Pulling in investors! Hurry.

402
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,240
Alright!

403
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,616
Brother Jiemin,

404
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:28,840
