407
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,120
Please.

408
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:40,360
Jingsheng, this is hard to come by.

409
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:44,360
I will cherish it.

410
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:51,800
I thank everyone for their help.

411
00:18:51,840 --> 00:18:55,720
I, Yuanpei, will certainly fulfill the mission.

412
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:58,936
Master Cai, when do you plan to assume office?

413
