421
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,776
Everyone present, please help me think

422
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:23,176
who is able to take on this important task.

423
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:25,880
This liberal arts dean

424
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:28,936
must be sympathetic to you,

425
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:30,776
but also be of noble character and high prestige.

426
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,696
Must be a learned academic,

427
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:35,256
but also with the ability to charge through enemy lines.

428
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:37,256
Such a person is not easy to find.

429
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:39,176
I've thought of someone.

430
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:42,216
Chen Zhongfu, or Chen Duxiu.

431
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:46,296
This is a person who is leading the trends of today's China.

432
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:49,496
He is certain to be able to take on this important task.

433
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:51,960
I also thought of Chen Duxiu.

434
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:57,416
Are you know Chen Duxiu well?

435
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,856
Only as an acquaintance.

436
