444
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,336
Where is he living? Do you know?

445
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,296
I will ask around.

446
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:23,640
Yes. Please.

447
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:26,536
Zhongfu, listen to me. Zhongfu.

