455
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:45,976
That's for sure.

456
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:46,936
Huge potential market.

457
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,136
Definitely.

458
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,936
Now I believe the words you spoke last year.

459
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,976
Which words?

460
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,976
You said, give you ten years.

461
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:57,000
And you will change the thinking of our compatriots.

462
00:20:57,520 --> 00:21:00,760
Now it looks like it won't take ten years.

463
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,576
We must set up a banquet.

464
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:04,456
To celebrate.

465
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:04,936
Yes.

466
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,696
I will ask Xingang and Bailan to come.

467
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:07,176
Quickly.

468
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,520
Yes.

