497
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:39,080
Even now, I often see it in my dreams.

498
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:41,416
True, true.

499
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:44,296
At the time, if you hadn't given that shove...

500
00:23:44,320 --> 00:23:46,936
I would not be sitting in front of you today.

501
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:49,176
Dead as a doornail, long ago.

502
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,616
Brother Zhongfu,

503
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,856
you saved my life.

504
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,536
I have to properly thank you.

505
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:57,160
You're too kind. You're overstating it.

506
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,256
Twelve years ago,

507
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:02,360
I was the age you are now.

508
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,576
At that time,

509
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:06,056
