519
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:30,056
A breath of fresh air.

520
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:32,576
I read every issue of your magazine "New Youth."

521
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,616
With each reading, there's always something to be gained.

522
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,776
Sir, if you would like to submit a manuscript,

523
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:38,936
I would be extremely grateful.

524
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:43,240
That is a matter of course. Naturally I will contribute.

525
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:47,400
I came here today

526
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:51,736
to ask you for some help.

527
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:53,640
Please go on, sir.

528
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:55,976
Starting yesterday, I have been

529
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:59,480
formally appointed the president of Peking Univesity.

530
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:07,480
Take a look. Letter of appointment.

531
00:25:14,560 --> 00:25:17,000
Congratulations, sir.

532
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:25,816
I would like you to come to Peking University to be the Dean of Liberal Arts.

533
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:27,736
Lend me a hand.

534
00:25:27,760 --> 00:25:29,816
Lend Peking University a hand.

535
00:25:29,840 --> 00:25:33,880
I hope Brother Zhongfu would not decline.

536
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,616
I would like to thank Brother Jiemin for the support.

537
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:44,456
But this is very sudden.

538
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:47,080
