00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:02,216
democratic science?

544
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:07,400
I think this would be your best stage to do so.

545
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:11,096
Precisely because it's a serious responsibility,

546
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:14,440
I don't want to rashly accept an appointment.

547
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:17,496
After all, I haven't properly gone to university.

548
00:26:17,520 --> 00:26:20,616
And have no experience teaching or educating others.

549
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:21,896
An incompetent person who pretends to be competent

550
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,576
will only hinder the progress of their students.

551
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:26,616
If I actually got in the way of your grand undertaking,

552
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:28,856
there would be no greater crime.

553
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:33,176
Don't decline in such a rush.

554
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:36,296
It's true that this is very abrupt.

555
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:38,216
You can discuss this at your leisure

556
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,776
with friends and family and then make a decision.

557
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:45,336
I am indeed eager in my search for talent.

558
00:26:45,360 --> 00:26:47,416
I am determined to invite you

559
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:49,816
to Peking University and work together.

560
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:54,200
For China. For education in China.

561
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:58,776
For Master Cai to show such high regard for me,

562
00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:00,696
I am truly moved to tears.

563
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:03,736
If Peking University is to become China's highest educational institution,

564
00:27:03,760 --> 00:27:06,616
it will be the best platform to advocate for science and democracy.

565
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:09,176
If there is an opportunity to follow Brother Jiemin

566
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:12,376
to Peking University and collaborate on this endeavour,

567
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:16,400
it would be the blessing of three lifetimes, exactly what I've been looking for.

568
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:18,376
But to be quite honest,

569
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,176
in my heart,

570
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:22,216
I can't let go of my "New Youth."

571
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:25,496
This magazine is still a fledgling

572
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:27,336
that has just started picking up.

573
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,616
I came to Beijing this time

574
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:31,976
precisely because of the magazine. Looking for investors and resources.

575
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:33,256
A successful harvest.

576
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:35,416
Only just today, I've discussed

577
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:38,600
an investment of over a hundred thousand shares.

578
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:40,856
At a time like this,

579
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,616
if I leave "New Youth" behind without a care

580
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,136
to take a position at Peking University,

581
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:45,736
wouldn't I be letting down

582
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:48,136
everyone's deep regard?

583
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:51,656
It's true. I understand.

584
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:55,416
What you are saying is not without reason.

585
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:58,456
If the result of you coming to Peking University

586
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:01,096
is the stoppage of the publication of "New Youth."

587
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:06,520
That's unacceptable.

588
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:12,056
Alright. I will now hurry back

589
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:15,256
to discuss how to solve the problem of "New Youth."

590
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:17,816
Zhongfu, my thinking is this.

591
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:20,856
Peking University must exist. "New Youth" must keep running.

592
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:24,216
I will definitely find a way to satisfy both requirements.

593
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:26,440
Alright. I'm leaving.

594
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,416
Brother Jiemin.

595
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:31,176
Brother Zhongfu.

596
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:35,960
Let's just call today my first of three humble visits to plead my case.

597
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:39,160
Ok. I will get going.

598
00:28:54,080 --> 00:28:55,736
Brother Mengzou,

599
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:58,296
I beg of you to handle the matter of signing the contracts.

600
00:28:58,320 --> 00:29:00,456
I have nothing to say to those business men.

601
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:03,080
I would only get in the way.

602
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:06,536
What? What do you mean?

603
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:08,616
You're not going?

604
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:11,416
Zhongfu, everyone is coming to see you.

605
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:12,856
Signing the contract is such an important thing.

606
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:15,960
If you don't show up, how will I explain it to them?

607
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:18,376
Just say I have an important meeting.

608
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:19,576
And it's the truth.

609
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:22,760
I need to go to Taoran Pavilion to see Quan Xuantong.

610
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:26,616
You're a really strange person.

611
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:28,136
It's snowing so hard.

612
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,176
And it's so cold.

613
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:31,336
What are you doing meeting someone at Taoran Pavilion?

614
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:33,016
To sample the northwesterly wind?

615
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:34,536
You don't understand.

616
00:29:34,560 --> 00:29:36,536
Heavy snow is romantic.

617
00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:39,176
This is the difference between a reader of books and a seller of books.

618
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:42,440
To make joy amidst misery is the essence of a scholar.

619
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:48,920
Not many people these days can keep in tune with such highbrow sentiments.

620
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:50,776
I surmise

621
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,936
Master Qian will not be singing the same tune.

622
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,296
And I surmise

623
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:57,720
at this very moment Qian Xuantong is already on his way there.

624
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:59,816
Zhongfu. Zhongfu.

625
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,816
Don't, Zhongfu.

626
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:04,920
No, if you leave, what do I do?

627
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,656
Brother Zhongfu!

628
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:17,576
Deqian, is that you?

629
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:20,056
I've been looking forward to meeting you. Your reputation preceeds you.

630
00:30:20,080 --> 00:30:23,240
Today, I finally see your face in person.

631
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:26,616
Myriad entities have different forms, but they are the same in essence.

632
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:28,936
Though in the corners of the world, we have never met,

633
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,456
we have long since been alike in spirit.

634
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,336
This is true.

635
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:33,903
{\an8}[Qian Xuantong, styled Deqian: Peking University professor]

636
00:30:31,127 --> 00:30:32,857
I am a faithful reader of "New Youth"

637
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:35,576
and a die-hard supporter of you, Chen Duxiu.

638
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:37,576
Deqian, you are too modest.

639
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:38,376
How is it?

640
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,856
To meet at Taoran pavilion in the snow today.

641
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,056
You don't find it odd?

642
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:43,336
To see Taoran in the snow?

643
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:44,456
'Elegant' is the only word for it.

644
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,416
How can it be odd?

645
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:47,560
You don't find it cold?

646
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:50,936
To meet brother Zhongfu is to be bathed in spring wind.

647
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,536
Any chill is entirely absent.

648
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,216
We are indeed fellow travellers.

649
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,656
We have another fellow traveller.

650
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,616
Let me introduce you.

651
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:58,136
This is Liu Bannong.

652
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,176
Literary translator.

653
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:02,456
and famed writer of the "Mandarin Ducks and Butterflies" school of fiction.

654
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,656
Bannong,

655
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:06,056
I've read many of your translations of European fiction.

656
00:31:06,080 --> 00:31:07,816
It has benefited me a great deal.

657
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:09,176
Compared to you, sir,

658
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:12,520
I am but a handful of soil next to Mount Tai.

659
00:31:12,560 --> 00:31:13,576
Why are the people in Beijing

660
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:16,040
all so modest?

661
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,496
Brother Zhongfu, let's talk in the pavilion.

662
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:19,256
Certainly.

663
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,416
Speaking of Taoran Pavilion,

664
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,496
among the most famous of its associations

665
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:24,136
is the composition by Jiang Zao, "Taoran Pavilion."

666
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,736
Reportedly, he often invited

667
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:27,576
scholars and literati, colleagues and close friends

668
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:30,040
to come here to feast and compose poetry.

669
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:43,976
Sure enough, it's a peaceful world in the world of mortals.

670
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:46,296
It's a pity, wine is left out today!

671
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:49,176
Brother Zhongfu has come, how can there be no wine?

672
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:52,200
Someone come! Bring wine!

673
00:31:53,760 --> 00:31:55,960
Come, come.

674
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,456
This wine is Shaoxing yellow wine.

675
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,616
That's right. My hometown's Shaoxing yellow wine.

676
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:26,776
After it's heated up, use a quilt to wrap it.

677
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,920
It's sent over by a rickshaw.

678
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:32,456
Deqian, Bannong, you guys really used your heart.

679
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,976
I'm moved, I'm moved.

680
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,056
I'm waiting for my yellow daisies at home to ripen.

681
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:39,016
We'll get drunk together and have a good time.

682
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:43,416
Good! Today there's you, there's snow,

683
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:47,976
there's Shaoxing yellow wine, there's a qin, there's poetry, there's red plums.

684
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:51,096
Having intimate friends in high mountains and rivers. It is indeed elegant.

685
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:52,216
Come.

686
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:54,120
Let us first toast a cup.

687
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:09,496
How is it?

688
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:10,840
Warm!

689
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,200
Come.

690
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:17,176
Banong, weren't you at Shanghai?

691
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,616
How come you also came to Beijing?

692
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,520
Is it to keep up with the latest fashion?

693
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,456
Peking University is making reforms.

694
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:25,240
I was thinking of coming over to apply for a teaching job.

695
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:28,136
Is this Beijing so attractive

696
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:30,536
to cultural people?

697
00:33:30,560 --> 00:33:32,056
It's strange to say that

698
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:34,056
at present, these scholars,

699
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:35,256
once arrived, won't leave.

700
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:37,176
They rush in like ducks,

701
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:40,376
no matter how poorly they live here.

702
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:41,336
Why is that?

703
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:43,576
High culture, low culture.

704
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:46,680
Dragons and fishes jumbled together, all embracing each other.

705
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:50,440
The opportunities and risks coexist.

706
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:52,440
Come.

707
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,880
Brother Zhongfu.

708
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,936
This "New Youth"

709
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:15,656
is like the fire of today's winter day.

710
00:34:15,680 --> 00:34:18,056
It ignited the light of hope of revitalizing China.

711
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:21,960
We are all followers of this torch.

712
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:24,136
This time Duxiu comes to Beijing

713
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:26,376
to pay his respects to all of you,

714
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,896
to help "New Youth"

715
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:30,216
to make its fire burn brighter.

716
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:31,736
An unshirkable responsibility.

717
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:34,200
Come.

718
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,696
Only, Brother Zhongfu, have you thought about

719
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:45,788
having "New Youth" move to Beijing.

720
00:34:48,071 --> 00:34:49,733
Beijing.

721
00:34:49,757 --> 00:34:52,136
Can "New Youth" gain a footing in Beijing?

722
00:34:52,160 --> 00:34:53,016
Of course.

723
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:54,536
More than gain a footing,

724
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:59,880
to be based in Beijing, we can look at the whole country and develop it.

725
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:03,976
Come, today we are not going home until we're drunk!

726
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,720
Okay! Cheers. Come.

727
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,576
Excuse me, may I ask

728
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:53,336
Is the guest home?

729
00:35:53,360 --> 00:35:56,696
Yes. However, he came home pretty late last night.

730
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:58,136
It seems like he drank a little too much.

731
00:35:58,160 --> 00:35:59,736
I reckon he's still not up at this time.

732
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,480
Let me call for you

733
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,616
Don't wake him up too loudly.

734
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:06,296
Let him sleep a while more.

735
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,176
Continue.

736
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,840
Alright.

737
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:35,480
Cabinet minister Cai.

738
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,136
I am Cai Yuanpei.

739
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,496
It's really you!

740
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:41,896
Y-you, what is this you are doing?

741
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,416
Zhongfu is resting.

742
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:45,480
I am waiting for him here.

743
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:47,336
How can this be allowed?

744
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:49,736
How can we allow you to be so condescending to simple men like this?

745
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,560
I'll call him, I'll call him.

746
00:37:51,920 --> 00:37:52,536
Zhongfu!

747
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,176
Don't, don't, don't.

748
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:53,656
Zhongfu!

749
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:55,416
Don't, don't wake him up.

750
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:56,776
Let him sleep a while more.

751
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,736
I can't, I can't.

752
00:37:57,760 --> 00:38:01,800
I see that you look very familiar.

753
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:05,336
Cabinet minister Cai, your humble servant Wang Mengzou.

754
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:07,176
Wang Mengzou... I know.

755
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:08,776
Scholar of Anhui province's Jixi county.

756
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,536
Director of Yadong county's library.

757
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:12,216
That library of yours is taken care of really well.

758
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:13,656
You overpraise.

759
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:14,376
Zhongfu.

760
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,120
Brother Jiemin.

761
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:21,560
Zhongfu, Zhongfu, the floor below has people.

762
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,296
I apologize, Brother Jiemin.

763
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,576
I drank too much yesterday.

764
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:28,216
Quick, enter the room.

765
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:28,936
Come, come, come.

766
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:30,456
Enter quickly, don't catch a cold.

767
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,256
Forgive me, forgive me.

768
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:31,576
Don't catch a cold.

769
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:33,096
Forgive me, sir.

770
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:33,656
Please sit, sir.

771
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:34,376
You sit, you sit.

772
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:35,416
I'll offer tea to you.

773
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,920
You take a seat first.

774
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:43,800
You guys chat first, I'm going to handle some matters.

775
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,840
Cabinet minister Cai, it was nice to meet you, nice to meet you.

776
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:51,176
Sir, drink tea.

777
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:53,480
No need, I'm eating peanuts.

778
00:39:10,640 --> 00:39:14,376
Boldly paid a visit, disturbed your rest.

779
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,976
Where?

780
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,976
I just wanted to tell you

781
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:20,376
Me and Cabinet Minister of Education Fan Yuanlian,

782
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:22,136
as well as colleagues of Peking University,

783
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:24,056
after the negotiations feel

784
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:25,656
you are able to have "New Youth"

785
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:27,640
brought to Peking University to manage.

786
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,096
At the same time,

787
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:31,576
"New Youth" can also

788
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:34,056
implement a lecture on editing for colleagues at Peking University.

789
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:35,496
If this happens then,

790
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:38,056
"New Youth" can have Peking University

791
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:40,456
treated as something to give publicity to Mr. Science and Mr. Democracy,

792
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,696
an exceptionally good platform.

793
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:47,320
With this, we will promote and spread the New Culture Movement.

794
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:53,960
I still need to tell you,

795
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:58,456
the head of humanities course's monthly income is three hundred silver dollars.

796
00:39:58,480 --> 00:40:00,456
Your whole family can go up north,

797
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:02,760
settle down in Beijing.

798
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:11,080
Make up your mind. Come to Peking University.

799
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:16,520
I sincerely need your help.

800
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:20,296
Honorable Cai, inviting me so kindly like this,

801
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:23,176
Duxiu is endlessly grateful.

802
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:26,776
Speaking truthfully, these two days have been a rush of excitement.

803
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,760
Cannot sleep soundly at night.

804
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,616
After drinking some wine yesterday night,

805
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:32,856
only then have I felt I had a good sleep.

806
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:36,216
It's just that, the matter of "New Youth" entering Beijing,

